{"tid":1795762,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"依家讀緊中學嘅唔該努力讀，Asso簡直係地獄！","createTime":"2019-12-24T07:04:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T05:47:23.000Z","uid":328505,"like":41,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"aee3546ec2241f10977836e33ede5aba8531e922","tid":1795762,"uid":328505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:04:37.000Z","msg":"背景：2019文憑試唔夠分入八大，所以依家做緊太空人。<br />\n<br />\n由於我讀工商管理副學士，所以喺製衣業訓練局上堂，呢間校舍喺一間工業大廈入面，可想而知學習環境有幾差。<br />\n<br />\n副學士係唔會有任何體育設施。有人可能反駁太空人可以用港大體育設施，但係薄扶林距離九龍灣咁遠，邊會得閒去。<br />\n<br />\n副學士比起大學生另一樣明顯分別就係冇宿舍！冇宿舍對於住得遠嘅人係超級痛苦。每日返學（我住天水圍）都要用三個鐘嚟搭車，嘥咗勁多時間，車費差唔多每日$50。仲要成日冇位坐，企成個鐘，企到腳都斷😭。<br />\n<br />\n副學士係冇canteen，得間爛鬼咖啡店，所以要食飯就要去德福，伙食費貴過大學生好多。<br />\n<br />\n另外，讀書方面，副學生嘅世界原來有不少學霸，佢哋原本係讀傳統名校，不過衰咗中文，先要紆尊降貴入嚟。所以根本比佢哋屌打，尤其係英文😔。<br />\n<br />\nAsso仔注定俾人睇唔起。好記得有一次去買嘢時同某位店員吹水，以下係我哋嘅對話：<br />\n店員：Er你依家讀緊中學呀？<br />\n我：我啱啱考完DSE，即將畢業。<br />\n店員：咦！咁即係下年入大學㗎啦喎！<br />\n我：Er...我邊入到呀？<br />\n店員：（好驚訝+超大聲）唔係呀？入唔到！<br />\n附近啲店員同啲客全部望住我，嗰刻真係想搵窿捐😢<br />\n<br />\n最後，副學士啲女同學差唔多全部都係豬扒，因為靚嗰啲已經全部上晒大學，日日對住佢哋上堂真係好辛苦🤢<br />\n<br />\n喺度真心奉勸各位中讀緊中學嘅，唔該努力讀書，直入大學。唔好好似我咁要做太空人！😩"},{"pid":"b4ee067599011076d2e8f69d9fcfe2089e98cc99","tid":1795762,"uid":69140,"like":12,"dislike":7,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:06:40.000Z","msg":"抵撚死"},{"pid":"0911ebc56c81acab79cba684480de89f3fac95d0","tid":1795762,"uid":9315,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:07:32.000Z","msg":"冇料學人嫌三嫌四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"359aa68ff795a986c808ce69f4eb202eb9b8064e","tid":1795762,"uid":275560,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:14:41.000Z","msg":"。。有冇咁誇張"},{"pid":"0f4bd3c78e37f905f50f5a10d9d970f2401b99c4","tid":1795762,"uid":328505,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"b4ee067599011076d2e8f69d9fcfe2089e98cc99","tid":1795762,"uid":69140,"like":12,"dislike":7,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:06:40.000Z","msg":"抵撚死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:20:14.000Z","msg":"的確抵撚死，所以仲讀緊中學嘅唔好好以我咁，後悔一世"},{"pid":"0a645324fde3b0a263849d1f65d0c0d55b846c5f","tid":1795762,"uid":64071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:20:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f802df3d3737bd3999a8f87196cfc03cf1c14c4","tid":1795762,"uid":305553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:21:58.000Z","msg":"CITA<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca1d14b70bc99a13c83061b6ca3e01d23e2ed2b7","tid":1795762,"uid":188188,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:32:45.000Z","msg":"完全同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：cc"},{"pid":"067c93d7e9a91e6065e71f084fd246318b0c6908","tid":1795762,"uid":191527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:34:45.000Z","msg":"牙蘇仔畢業出黎注定乞食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e578ad118f1438117b25493a1504551043ba53f7","tid":1795762,"uid":34500,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:37:44.000Z","msg":"豬扒都係肉"},{"pid":"6e214a7a930a76f05320f17f684e08b848258c6b","tid":1795762,"uid":259729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:41:02.000Z","msg":"年經"},{"pid":"dc2283e73e06ccf96b340cb79766f99050fec5cc","tid":1795762,"uid":154106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:44:01.000Z","msg":"投過胎，搵過第個父母去外國讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf80189ed5fbb74d19df0045bd44efbe38a4733","tid":1795762,"uid":123848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"s