\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d77baf5789a47accd676b9c413610536b719bbfc","tid":1795762,"uid":286206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T10:14:13.000Z","msg":"當然你本身語文差你仲要讀翻譯果D科就另計"},{"pid":"ac4dd31be0ab973a3b4df72b4fe100e3ceebfba2","tid":1795762,"uid":328505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8486e7e5ffefc130de13fc2f0aa77296414a1ba3","tid":1795762,"uid":241364,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T00:44:09.000Z","msg":"Asso仔係慘，但Po主我覺得你應該問問自己點解要讀Asso，你依家生活嘅意義同目標係乜。唔好掛住溝女，呢啲係假嘅。讀Asso係慘過正常U，但Asso亦都有Asso Life。搏得盡，佢會教識你好多人同事，尤其係點樣去對待學習呢件事。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T10:20:58.000Z","msg":"呢個post目的係提醒中學生要好好讀書，唔好好似我咁要做太空人（唔係搏同情）<br />\n<br />\n唔打算溝，但同啲靚嘅生物上堂，的確會精神啲！<br />\n<br />\nAsso令我尊嚴掃地，所以教識我要力爭上游！"},{"pid":"264f4b2e7f090f748f4940a706b7888f7dc11f70","tid":1795762,"uid":328505,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5d87e18feeaba3057ed6ff304b995a95ef3367c2","tid":1795762,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T01:11:25.000Z","msg":"on9 assohole都叫地獄<br />\nDSE一次考六科 每一科都起碼三年既野<br />\nasso？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T10:30:02.000Z","msg":"我嘅課程都要讀5科。<br />\n<br />\n但「地獄」嘅最大原因同課程無關，例如冇宿舍。"},{"pid":"b11980dccbec706156bb9def21f8796619627f58","tid":1795762,"uid":328505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"916a398fb4b25029e79891cd51e768b2ab87d2c4","tid":1795762,"uid":316227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T02:56:59.000Z","msg":"又唔覺Asso有咩問題喎<br />\n<br />\n利申讀緊BU CIE<br />\n有Gym 有泳池 老師nice 附近多嘢食 交通方便<br />\n讀完兩年正常都會上返到U<br />\n<br />\n利申full cert 不過想揀科讀 焗入Asso先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T10:32:37.000Z","msg":"BU CIE咁正，好羡慕😍"}]}